INTRODUCTION & PROBLEM STATEMENT

We consider a single objective minimization problem defined over a compact set X. The deterministic
dâ€“dimensional objective function f : x âˆˆ X âŠ‚ â„œd â†’ f (x) âˆˆ â„œ can only be observed with noise from a
